{"id": "art-119", "label": "Art. 119", "title": "Art. 119", "slug": "art-119", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1036282300\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1264\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1036282300\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 119 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1374338598\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1263\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1374338598\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Angajatorul are obliga&#355;ia de a &#355;ine la locul\nde munc&#259; definit potrivit art. 16<sup>1</sup> eviden&#355;a orelor de\nmunc&#259; prestate zilnic de fiecare salariat, cu eviden&#355;ierea orelor de\nîncepere &#351;i de sfâr&#351;it ale programului de lucru, &#351;i de a supune\ncontrolului inspectorilor de munc&#259; aceast&#259; eviden&#355;&#259;, ori de\ncâte ori se solicit&#259; acest lucru.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1567376970\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1262\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1567376970\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Pentru salaria&#355;ii mobili &#351;i salaria&#355;ii\ncare desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; munc&#259; la domiciliu, angajatorul &#355;ine\neviden&#355;a orelor de munc&#259; prestate zilnic de fiecare salariat în\ncondi&#355;iile stabilite cu salaria&#355;ii prin acord scris, în func&#355;ie\nde activitatea specific&#259; desf&#259;&#351;urat&#259; de c&#259;tre\nace&#351;tia.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 2:Munca suplimentar&#259;</span></b></p>"}